data.description: Corner condo has contemporary features that will make you feel right at home. 3 bd/2 full baths.  1,725 sq ft of living. Assigned parking. Community pool/tennis. Spacious kitchen: Wolf cooktop, oven & vent hood. Granite counters. Beautiful dark wood flooring on 1st floor. There is a bedroom and full bath downstairs! Upstairs has wow factor with new carpet sliding closet doors, well lit bathroom, balcony +2 BD. Fence patio with gate. $5,000 credit for 6 months of HOA fees. Work scheduled by hoa for exterior.
